class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-is_sat\"><a href=\"#val-is_sat\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> is_sat : <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> bool</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-is_unsat\"><a href=\"#val-is_unsat\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> is_unsat : <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> bool</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-admissible\"><a href=\"#val-admissible\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> admissible : <span><span class=\"label\">mode</span>:<a href=\"../Approx/index.html#type-t\">Approx.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"#type-t\">t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> bool</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>admissible ~mode result</code> determines whether a branch should be taken based on the solver result and approximation mode.</p><p>The decision matrix:</p><ul><li><code>Sat, _</code>: Always take the branch (definitely feasible)</li><li><code>Unsat, _</code>: Never take the branch (definitely infeasible)</li><li><code>Unknown, OX</code>: Take the branch (over-approximate: don't miss paths)</li><li><code>Unknown, UX</code>: Don't take the branch (under-approximate: avoid possibly unsatisfiable paths)</li></ul></div></div>"}